          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='flex items-start gap-3'>
          <div
            class='w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5'
          >
            <span class='text-xs font-semibold text-primary'>2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='font-medium text-foreground'>Practice regularly</p>
            <p class='text-sm text-muted-foreground'>Apply what you learn by
